SQL_STMT_U.val: select count (*) from (select distinct trim(wb.wk_categorie_1), trim(wb.wk_categorie_2), trim(wb.wk_categorie_3), trim(wb.wk_categorie_4), trim(wb.wk_waarde_2) from :1 wb where wb.wk_terminal = ~2 and wb.wk_soort = 'VRTX' and wb.wk_waarde_1 = 1)

select distinct trim(wb.wk_categorie_1), trim(wb.wk_categorie_2), trim(wb.wk_categorie_3), trim(wb.wk_categorie_4), trim(wb.wk_waarde_1), trim(wb.wk_waarde_2), trim(wb.wk_waarde_3) , trim(wb.wk_waarde_4) from WERKBESTAND wb where wb.wk_terminal = ~1 and wb.wk_soort = 'VRTX' and wb.wk_waarde_1 in (1,2) and (trim(wb.wk_categorie_4)=~2 OR wb.wk_waarde_2<0) order by trim(wb.wk_categorie_1), trim(wb.wk_categorie_2), trim(wb.wk_categorie_3), trim(wb.wk_categorie_4), trim(wb.wk_waarde_1)
